{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Subtle_Exchange",
  "title": "A Subtle Exchange",
  "summary": "In the domed botanical garden behind Tredo's Botanicals, the pirate captain Nastaran Zohreh waits to meet a well-connected infochant, introduced through the Ithorian black marketeer Tredo. The double-mouthed Ithorian Rixt arrives, and over shared Ithorian liquor and Corellian whisky the two feel each other out and strike a working arrangement: Nastaran's crew will cut Rixt in on the spoils of their piracy and use him as a fence for rarities, while Rixt offers a target of his own near Tatooine -- a delay on a shipping lane that will help him quietly reclaim something that is rightfully his. Before leaving, Nastaran also commissions Rixt for a personal matter: to discreetly uncover the full name and employer of a stiff, arrogant, cybernetically-augmented human she met named Elias, whom she suspects of Black Sun ties. Rixt, treating the whole affair as a worthy game, accepts the challenge, and Nastaran departs through the leaves, leaving him the bottle of Ithorian liquor as a gift.",
